title: The Complete Squidward SpongeBob SquarePants Timeline

media:group.media:title: The Complete Squidward SpongeBob SquarePants Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire timeline of Squidward Tentacles from SpongeBob SquarePants. Voiced by Rodger Bumpass, we look at Squidward's history, his past and future. Taking a look at the full SpongeBob SquarePants episodes, I've put Squidward's life in chronological order. From season 1 to newest SpongeBob SquarePants season. I talk about how Squidward met Spongebob and Patrick, Spongebob's house and discuss the spin-off show Kamp Koral and the SpongeBob movies.

We also look at the funniest SpongeBob SquarePants moments from Patrick, Squidward, Mr Krabs, Plankton and Mrs Puff. As well as other SpongeBob SquarePants characters from Bikini Bottom.

Special thanks to @PhantomStrider
